{"tid":843193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隨地大小便奪命　大陸仔撒尿跌入池塘溺斃","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T03:39:26.000Z","uid":122,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb731e12b01848b4c4e8268c1e74898782dd978","tid":843193,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"中國又發生隨地便溺的奪命悲劇，湖南長沙一名女子周五（28日）帶著兩名孩子外出遊玩，期間6歲兒子尿急，她因為要叫車，便叫兒子到池塘邊小便，沒想到兒子不慎跌入水中溺斃。女子強調，兒子當時是在自己視線範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，當時有聽到小孩的呼救聲，但跑到池塘附近時，呼救聲已經聽了，見到有人下水救人，他自己也下水協助。約2、3分鐘後，他們終找到遇溺的男童。<br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶，江西贛州早前也有一名6歲女童，突然間跑到大馬路邊脫褲子就地解放，沒想到一輛中型巴士沒注意到女童，直接從女童身上輾過，把她輾斃。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"5c25117c8b15e09d1d31c75f5909484c3e5c4ac9","tid":843193,"uid":103294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:21:51.000Z","msg":"他只是個孩子啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a870b297199d924533e8ff66d269fc1d7818575b","tid":843193,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d0f2e867070a6f6ffdf34cbd5fb83f904ca7b16","tid":843193,"uid":113335,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:24:12.000Z","msg":"唔係話咩黑心<br />\n咁既智力 柯個尿都可以浸死 真係唔死都冇用"},{"pid":"08f7870c45dfa6000d9288d81bf1e9f8bd5d8028","tid":843193,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07758b95e78cc5b5911c7ffc2595e38f493e88e6","tid":843193,"uid":190181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"民以尿為天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f54fa9bbd53c832b8942ab20c5b78be9c6acd87","tid":843193,"uid":174418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"意外"},{"pid":"273e6db05159a1e86bb527146b6890643b5968b2","tid":843193,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a870b297199d924533e8ff66d269fc1d7818575b","tid":843193,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"稍安毋躁，你的呼救聲已經聽到了，請保持安靜，謝謝"},{"pid":"9c4e8abbfcb303a32aba815de856d5452cdbe90c","tid":843193,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"小处不可随便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}